4. 🧬 Perceived Color ID (PCID System)

Create a new standard like Pantone codes:

Format:

CF-[hash]-[intent]-[variant]

Example:

CF-9X2A-LUX-MIDNIGHT
CF-7K1B-MED-STERILE-BLUE
CF-3F9Q-WARN-RED-HIGHVIS

These are:
	•	Stable identifiers
	•	Context-aware
	•	Expandable

